data.title: Nobel Prize in Literature
data.meta_description: Nobel Prize in Literature - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides a list of winners of the Nobel Prize in Literature from 1901 to 2017. It begins with background on the Nobel Prize in Literature, which is awarded annually by the Swedish Academy to an author who has produced work that is considered to have conferred the greatest benefit on humanity. The bulk of the document consists of a table listing each winner's name, nationality, and notable literary works from 1901 to 2017.
